ning data (specified by index) or None at end of epoch\r\n        def __len__(self): # returns number of training batches availible\r\n        def on_epoch_end(self): # called at the end of each epoch\r\n\r\nTo use this you can set this up so that the current training data is stored in som class local variable at the end of each epoch you get a call to `on_epoch_end` where you can replace the training data with new data. If you need access to the model either pass a reference in before calling fit or store it in some scope accessible from the generator class.\r\n\r\nDo you follow?\r\n\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/autonomio/talos/issues/comments/467873824/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"JohanMollevik","id":43040671,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQzMDQwNjcx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/43040671?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik","html_url":"https://github.com/JohanMollevik","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/JohanMollevik/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/autonomio/talos/issues/comments/467949633","html_url":"https://github.com/autonomio/talos/issues/237#issuecomment-467949633","issue_url":"ht